#Text=The Sacramento Kings ( 24 - 31 ) defeated the Denver Nuggets ( 22 - 35 ) 114 - 110 on Tuesday .

#Text=A fast - paced , high - scoring affair befitting of both team 's explosive offenses and equally vulnerable defenses effectively ended with a highlight defensive play from the best player on the court in DeMarcus Cousins .
#Text=Although they entered the final period on the short end of a 91 - 77 score , Denver mounted an impressive rally that eventually saw them take a 104 - 103 lead on a three - pointer from D.J .
#Text=Augustin with 4:5 remaining .
#Text=The two teams traded the advantage and also drew even multiple times over nearly the next four minutes .

#Text=After Sacramento managed to open up a slightly comfortable four - point lead , Nikola Jokic made a surprising three - pointer with 10 seconds remaining to close the deficit to a single point once again .
#Text=Darren Collison made only one of two free throws following a take foul on him by Augustin , leaving Denver with nine seconds to tie or hit a likely game - winning trey .

#Text=Darrell Arthur appeared to have a clear path to a tying layup after breaking free down court on the inbounds pass , but Cousins made a terrific play to strip the ball and secure the hard - fought victory .
#Text=Cousins unsurprisingly led the way for the visitors with 39 points , nine rebounds , two assists , a steal and a pair of blocks .
#Text=Rudy Gay was a distant second with a nevertheless solid 16 points , 10 rebounds , four assists , four steals and three blocks .
#Text=While no other starter managed double - digit scoring , Rajon Rondo did hand out 12 assists , while two reserves had productive outings .

#Text=Omri Casspi contributed a near double - double with 14 points , nine rebounds , two assists and a steal , while Willie Cauley-Stein pitched in with 10 points , five rebounds , an assist , a steal and two blocks .
#Text=Collison and Marco Belinelli supplied a pair of nine - point efforts as well , with the former adding five assists , four rebounds and a steal .
#Text=Sacramento remains in third place in the Western Conference 's Pacific Division , and three and a half games behind the eighth - seeded Houston Rockets .
#Text=They 're home on Thursday to face off against the San Antonio Spurs .
#Text=Denver 's first unit was led by Danilo Gallinari 's 17 points , but he could only add a rebound , an assist and a steal .
#Text=Nikola Jokic filled out the stat sheet in much more impressive fashion , totaling 13 points , 13 boards , six assists and a pair of steals .
#Text=Kenneth Faried tallied 13 points of his own , and also chipped in seven rebounds , an assist , a steal and a block .
#Text=Emmanuel Mudiay supplied 11 points , four assists , a steal and a block .
#Text=Meanwhile , a Nuggets bench that impressively posted 52 points on the night was paced by 18 from Will Barton , which he complemented with six rebounds and four assists .
#Text=Arthur had a solid 14 points , five rebounds , four assists and a pair of steals , his final rejected shot notwithstanding .
#Text=Augustin and Joffrey Lauvergne registered a pair of 10 - point efforts , with the former adding three rebounds , four assists and a steal , and the latter hauling in six boards .
#Text=The Nuggets remain in fourth place in the Western Conference 's Northwest Division .
#Text=They face off against the Clippers in Los Angeles on Thursday .
